 "remarks": "Available for immediate occupancy! Fully furnished with flexible lease terms available. This meticulously reimagined English manor was taken down to the studs and completely rebuilt in 2014. Privately set at the end of a cul-de-sac and perched atop 2.50 acres of manicured lawns, it captures distant views of Cos Cob Harbor and Long Island Sound. A state-of-the-art Crestron system provides effortless, whole-house control of lighting, shades, climate, audio/visual, and security. Refined formal rooms, a bespoke gourmet kitchen, and dual terraces open seamlessly to the level grounds. The home also features a finished lower level with playroom and fitness area, a third-floor bonus room, and a fourth-floor tower room with spectacular water views. Private water access.",
